To evaluate deeper programmatic logic, we utilized a novel metric CodeBLEU @ren2020codebleu on the fully reconstructed files to assess structural integrity via AST matching and variable routing through data-flow analysis. The final CodeBLEU scores and its 4 individual components' scores are shown in @codebleu-scores. Since long prefixes and suffixes are stitched to model output, the original CodeBLEU scores are close to 1. Therefore, they are inverted using the formula $N' = 100(1 - N)$.

